      "content": "nothing has worked. every doctor just wants to add another pill to the pile and hope for the best, but it never actually helps the burning. it's just a cycle of hoping for a miracle and then being disappointed when the pain comes back even worse. it's exhausting to keep existing just to wait for the next flare up. i look at it like... if i could just hit a stop button, wouldn't that be the most compassionate thing for me? for anyone in this much pain?",
